Text:
This torrent works great!...But it's missing instructions which will make it impossible for people to install...I found them on another torrent. 
=================================

Installation and Activation:

1)Click and drag Fantastical to your Applications folder
2)Start the CORE keygen
3)Enter your name
4)Click the Generate button
5)Click the Patch button
6)Close the keygen and block the app with Little Snitch
7)Start Fantastical
8)Click on the app icon in your menubar (right side)
9)Click on the Gear icon (lower right side of the window)
10)Click on License
11)Enter the name you used in the keygen (license is already entered)
Is compatible with mountain lion? Thanks.
